<subSubSection pageId="19" pageNumber="503" type="distribution">
<caption ID-DOI="http://doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.6458660" ID-Zenodo-Dep="6458660" httpUri="https://zenodo.org/record/6458660/files/figure.png" inLine="true" pageId="19" pageNumber="503" targetBox="[136,726,1354,1769]" targetPageId="19">
<paragraph blockId="19.[750,1341,1344,1772]" pageId="19" pageNumber="503">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[750,926,1581,1614]" pageId="19" pageNumber="503">Distribution.</emphasis>
Currently known only from type locality in Soberania National Park, 
<collectingCountry box="[750,864,1664,1693]" name="Panama" pageId="19" pageNumber="503">Panama</collectingCountry>
